Steps for making an app:
prerequisite: a)Basic Understanding of Java(classes,objects and Inheritance),DBMS,PHP,SQL.
              b)PC with minimum 4GB RAM and Android Device.
1.first Install Android Studio and java JDK
2.go to the new project.
3.write your application name.
4.Select minimum SDK
5.select blank activity.
6.finally start coding.(start making app).

XML is used for design part(TextView and color it, position it, margin it, padding it etc.).
JAVA is used for inner part of the app,it interact with activity.(how activity functioned).
